{"tid":351750,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"看完荒野求生節目後獨闖沙漠 男子被困獲救","createTime":"2017-08-08T10:14:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-08T11:44:58.000Z","uid":55981,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c9f397f226449a125b32b0a3b91a084d4b3105a3","tid":351750,"uid":55981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T10:14:51.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國江蘇省一名19歲的薛姓男子，因為看了荒野求生節目，心中燃起雄心壯志，於是便輕裝獨闖新疆沙漠，結果徒步走了2天，他就被高溫熱到無法前進，困在沙漠中，只好緊急打電話叫救援；所幸救援隊伍即時趕到，救回薛男一命。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpSkqgKy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpSkqgKy.jpg&h=b1db9caf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據中國《央視新聞》報導，當地警方表示，當時接獲薛男求救電話，他在電話中說，在沙漠迷路了，沒有水源，已經快不行了；透過訊號鎖定薛男位置後，當地各單位派出共11人的救援隊伍，展開了聯合救援行動。 <br />\n<br />\n新疆兵團醫生馬建峰說，當時天氣很熱，他們扛著氧氣筒，走了3公里的路，沙子很燙腳，且路上都是荊棘，非常不好走，在經過2個小時後，終於找到薛男。馬建峰說，當下薛男嚴重脫水，肌肉無力，心跳非常快，意識還開始不清楚。 <br />\n<br />\n幸運的是，經過救治，薛男目前已脫離險境。<br />\n<br />\n薛男說，他第一次到新疆，因為看了國外的探險節目「荒野求生」後，沒有準備太多，就徒步走進新疆塔克拉瑪干沙漠探險，到最後走不動了，覺得站起來就兩眼發昏，看什麼東西都是兩個形狀，然後就倒了。 <br />\n<br />\n《央視新聞》報導此新聞時，官方微博還提醒眾人：「冒險精神誠可貴，做好充足準備再出發！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpxrcemi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpxrcemi.jpg&h=0be2d8a1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"36f3431bca6ebb29147d573a830b835b33476749","tid":351750,"uid":55981,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T10:15:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/5KMlaGC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F5KMlaGC.jpg&h=31d33294&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e914377391fc9986d427fa8990fbb82e13c261bd","tid":351750,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T10:16:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b306201cc1faacbc9b4a290480ca8736d3b97ce1","tid":351750,"uid":17822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T10:16:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92f4aad88e13717512904277f31a907615352bfe","tid":351750,"uid":53374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T10:20:18.000Z","msg":"on9蝗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccf8088e3690cbf770f287feef7db8def68acbdc","tid":351750,"uid":65952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T10:26:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/5KMlaGC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F5KMlaGC.jpg&h=31d33294&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"786210ab900e350b222f83f82e279a36aa9d310a","tid":351750,"uid":61653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T11:31:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/5KMlaGC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F5KMlaGC.jpg&h=31d33294&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一睇就個photo shop<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c1f94ceab474d81a974c06e267deaa7b936a64f","tid":351750,"uid":11753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T11:35:47.000Z","msg":"This on9 仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d0af2d10e178349740b31f368d7d35bf600c4a7","tid":351750,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T11:39:10.000Z","msg":"睇咗&quot;人在野&quot;個節目"},{"pid":"75d0018fb05fd389ec1adcdc303775deaa4cceaf","tid":351750,"uid":67551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T11:39:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://